will furnish the information desired.
When there is no law upon the subject, the County Superintendent, the Board of School Examiners, a teacher, a
number of teachers, or any friend of education, may issue,
through the county press, a call for a meeting of the teachers, and submit the matter to them for their consideration
and action; or one or more individuals may, at their own
